---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import slide1 from '../../assets/slide-final1.jpg';
import slide2 from '../../assets/slide-final2.jpg';
import slide3 from '../../assets/slide-final3.jpg';
import slide4 from '../../assets/slide-final4.jpg';
import slide5 from '../../assets/slide-final5.jpg';
---
<section class="
        container mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-7 pt-0
        lg:min-h-[500px] content-center font-devblog
        prose lg:prose-xl
        prose-headings:font-devblog-space prose-headings:mt-5 prose-headings:text-devblog-dark prose-headings:font-bold lg:prose-h1:text-7xl prose-h1:mt-0 prose-heading:transition-all prose-heading:duration-300  
        prose-p:text-devblog-primary/50 dark:prose-p:text-white/70 prose-p:mb-0 prose-p:transition-all prose-p:duration-300
        prose-img:mt-0 prose-img:mb-0  
        dark:prose-headings:text-white
    ">
    <h1>DevBlog.</h1>
    <p>
        Acá encontrarás inspiración, guías y recursos para llevar tus proyectos web y de aplicaciones al siguiente nivel.
    </p>
    <h1><span class="gradient-underline"><span>"Descubrí tips, tutoriales y herramientas para mejorar tus proyectos de desarrollo web y apps."
    </span></span></h1>
</section>

<section class="my-10 flex justify-center gap-5 overflow-hidden py-4 sm:gap-10">
    <div class="relative w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-devblog-dark sm:w-3/12 rotate-2 rounded-[15px]">
        <Image src={slide1} width={800} alt="" class="object-cover image-shine h-[200px] md:h-[500px]" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-devblog-dark sm:w-3/12 -rotate-2 rounded-[15px]">
        <Image src={slide5} width={800} alt="" class="object-cover image-shine h-[200px] md:h-[500px]" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-devblog-dark sm:w-3/12 rotate-2 rounded-[15px]">
        <Image src={slide3} width={800} alt="" class="object-cover image-shine h-[200px] md:h-[500px]" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-devblog-dark sm:w-3/12  rotate-2 rounded-[15px]">
        <Image src={slide4} width={800} alt="" class="object-cover image-shine h-[200px] md:h-[500px]" />
    </div>
    <div class="relative w-44 flex-none overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-devblog-dark sm:w-3/12 -rotate-2 rounded-[15px]">
        <Image src={slide2} width={800} alt="" class="object-cover image-shine h-[200px] md:h-[500px]" />
    </div>
</section>